{% doc %}
  @prompt
    "Create a new product section block named 'Live Personalization Preview.' The entire section must be contained within an element for a collapsible row, with the summary text being 'Customize Your Product Here.'
    1. Input Form Field and Data Persistence: Include a required, multi-line <textarea> input field for customer personalization. This text box must function as a line item property named properties to ensure data persistence to the cart. Set the field height to 5 rows and include a descriptive placeholder text. Crucially, the customer must be able to press enter to create new lines of text.
    2. Mockup Display and Data Sourcing: Position a product mockup display adjacent to the input field on desktop (and stacked on mobile) using appropriate responsive HTML/CSS structure. The image source for this mockup must be dynamically pulled from the product's metafield using the namespace custom and key mockup_image (Liquid syntax: product.metafields.custom.mockup_image). Use the Liquid image_url filter and include a necessary Liquid conditional check (if) and fallback if the metafield is empty.
    3. Text Overlay and Centering: Create a dynamically updated text overlay positioned absolutely over the entire area of the mockup image. This overlay must display the text entered by the customer in the textarea. The text overlay must be styled using CSS Flexbox properties (display: flex, align-items: center, justify-content: center) to achieve perfect horizontal and vertical centering over the image. The text within the overlay must also use text-align: center and must wrap lines appropriately.
    4. CSS Optimizations: Ensure the preview text overlay container uses the CSS properties white-space: pre-line and appropriate sizing/color settings for legibility against the mockup image., 5. Create an option for the customer to choose a font for the personalisation. The fonts are the following “Helvetica, New York, Abril Fatface, Anton, Archivo Black, Arial, Bagel Fat One, BEBAS NEUE, Caprasimo, Caveat, Chakra Petch, Courier New, DM Serif Text, Funnel Display, Gluten, Josefin Sans, Kaushan Script, Lobster Two, Nothing You Could Do, Pinyon Script”.
    6. Create an option for the customer to upload a file as a property for the input field., The input text for personalisation and the display it on the mockup picture is not working right, If the product metafield custom.color is White, Beige or Yellow the preview text color must be black, unless it must be the default color., Make a clickable text saying “Greek Fonts”. When you click it, a pop up while appear, displaying an image., Put numbers 1 to 20 at the left of the font names, in the font selector., Add the following text as a footnote at the bottom of the mockup picture with small size font. "The personalization preview is not accurate and should be used only for a general idea of the engraving, as it is a simulation that will not look exactly like the final product.", Give options to stylize the collapsable row, such as background color, border radius, border line color and thickness., Add an arrow at the right of the collapsable row to indicate if the row is open or close. Also give me stylise options when the cursor is hovering at the collapsable row., Add an arrow at the right of the collapsable row to indicate if the row is open or close. Also give me stylise options when the cursor is hovering over the collapsable row.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% liquid
  assign product_color = product.metafields.custom.color | downcase
  assign text_color = block.settings.preview_text_color
  
  if product_color == 'white' or product_color == 'beige' or product_color == 'yellow'
    assign text_color = '#000000'
  endif
%}

{% style %}
  .ai-live-preview-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-live-preview-details-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    border: {{ block.settings.collapsible_border_thickness }}px solid {{ block.settings.collapsible_border_color }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.collapsible_border_radius }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.collapsible_background_color }};
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-live-preview-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.collapsible_hover_background_color }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.collapsible_hover_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-live-preview-summary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    list-style: none;
    user-select: none;
    color: {{ block.settings.collapsible_text_color }};
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-live-preview-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-live-preview-summary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: {{ block.settings.collapsible_hover_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-live-preview-summary-{{ ai_gen_id }}::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .ai-live-preview-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 12px;
  }

  .ai-live-preview-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    stroke: {{ block.settings.arrow_color }};
  }

  .ai-live-preview-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover .ai-live-preview-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    stroke: {{ block.settings.arrow_hover_color }};
  }

  .ai-live-preview-details-{{ ai_gen_id }}[open] .ai-live-preview-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .ai-live-preview-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 0 16px 16px;
  }

